quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  15,26,Humne Insaan ko sadi (rotten) hui mitti ke sookhey gaarey (clay) se banaya
  15,27,Aur ussey pehle Jinno ko hum aag ki lapat se paida kar chuke thay
  15,28,Phir yaad karo us mauqe ko jab tumhare Rubb ne Farishton se kaha ke “ main sadi hui mitti ke sookhey gaarey se ek bashar paida kar raha hoon
  15,29,Jab main usey poora bana chukun aur us mein apni rooh se kuch phoonk doon to tum sab uske aagey sajde mein gir jana”
  15,30,Chunanchey tamaam Farishton ne sajda kiya
  15,31,"Siwaye Iblees ke, ke usne sajda karne walon ka saath dene se inkar kardiya"
  15,32,"Rubb ne pucha “ aey Iblis , tujhey kya hua ke tu nay sajda karne walon ka saath na diya?”"
  15,33,Usne kaha “mera yeh kaam nahin hai ke main is bashar ko sajda karoon jisey tu nay sadi hui mitti ke sookhey gaarey se paida kiya hai”
  15,34,Rubb ne farmaya “accha to nikal jaa yahan se kyunke tu mardood(accursed) hai
  15,35,Aur ab roz-e-jaza tak tujhpar lanat hai”
  15,36,"Usne arz kiya “mere Rubb, yeh baat hai to phir mujhey us roz tak ke liye mohlat de jabke sab Insaan dobara uthaye jayenge”"
  15,37,"Farmaya “ accha, tujhey mohlat hai"
  15,38,Us din tak jiska waqt humein maloom hai”
  15,39,"Woh bola “mere Rubb, jaisa tu nay mujhey behkaya usi tarah ab main zameen mein inke liye dil farebiyan paida karke in sabko behka dunga"
  15,40,Siwaye tere un bandon ke jinhein tu nay inmein se khaalis karliya ho”
  15,41,Farmaya “yeh raasta hai jo seedha mujh tak pahunchta hai
  15,42,"Beshak , jo mere haqiqi banday hain unpar tera bas na chalega. Tera bas to sirf un behke huey logon hi par chalega jo teri pairwi karein"
  15,43,Aur un sab ke liye jahannum ki waeed(destined) hai”
  15,44,"Yeh jahannum ( jiski waeed pairwan e Iblis ke liye ki gayi hai) uske saat (seven) darwaze hain, har darwaze keliye unmein se ek hissa makhsoos kardiya gaya hai"